      "comment": "PAW BASTOW (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (22.56) last time in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Has ability and looks hard to stop. PAW PASCAL (3) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (22.43) at Shepparton. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. PAW NORBERT (1) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 1.75 lengths 4th at Geelong (22.94). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can do much better this time. MOONLIGHT JAZZ (8) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
